## Implementation Details
**Location**: `untanglit/app/layout.tsx`

The SpeedInsights component is correctly implemented:
```tsx
import { SpeedInsights } from "@vercel/speed-insights/next"

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="en">
      <body>
        {children}
        <Analytics />
        <SpeedInsights />
      </body>
    </html>
  )
}
```

This is the recommended implementation for Next.js 16 (App Router), which:
- Uses the correct import path for Next.js 13.5+
- Places the component in the root layout
- Positions it within the body tag for proper initialization
- Requires no additional configuration or props

